The paper focuses on using deep convolutional neural networks to study the tuning landscape of sensory neurons, which falls under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational neuroscience (cs.NI).
